metadata.name: Dolly Factory
metadata.description:
This factory is a factory with a wide variety of parts.
There are many colors to produce each doll differently. Some have this color, some don't, it's a combination. This factory is unattended. Only a living doll. They will choose their own color. The division of departments will also change. And finally, this factory cannot be opened to anyone.
besides their own dolls.
